title: Murphy, Escobar become the latest surprise stars in October
text:
> Top News Murphy, Escobar become the latest surprise stars in October Kansas City Royals' Alcides Escobar, top, leaps to turn a double play over Toronto Blue Jays' Edwin Encarnacion during the fourth inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Championship Series on Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015, in Toronto. (Darren Calabrese/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT
